data.description: This inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bath home in the heart of Troy offers a contemporary living experience. The fully remodeled kitchen and bathrooms provide a modern touch, equipped with all appliances and a spacious pantry. The family room, with its vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace, creates a cozy and welcoming atmosphere. Outside, a fenced yard, stamped concrete patio, and porch offer a delightful outdoor oasis. The flexible layout includes an upstairs bedroom that could serve as a master with an ensuite. Located centrally, residents enjoy easy access to entertainment, restaurants, shopping, expressways, and the convenience of being in the acclaimed Troy School District. The open concept living adds to the home's appeal, providing a comfortable and stylish space for daily living and entertaining!
